better-foliage.Description: Improves the flora in the world. Very heavy, but very pretty. (Sane defaults set.)

client-tweaks.Description: Various client related fixes and tweaks, all in a handy menu.

custom-fov.Description: Removes dynamic FOV shifting due to ingame effects.

durability-show.Description: Toggle-able item/tool/armor durability HUD. Duplicates with RPG-HUD.

fancy-block-particles.Description: Caution: Resource heavy. Adds some flair to particle effects and animations. Highly configurable, costs fps.

faster-ladder-climbing.Description: Helps you control ladder climb speed and allows you to go a bit faster.

itemzoom.Description: Enable this if you like to get a closer look at item textures.

laggoggles.Description: ***Admin/diagnostic tool. Leave off unless asked to help test performance issues.

light-level-overlay-reloaded.Description: Smol light-level overlay if you aren't using Dynamic Surroundings.

minemenu.Description: Radial menu that can be used for command/keyboard shortcuts. Some keybinds cannot be added to radial menu.

mouse-tweaks.Description: Add extra mouse gestures for inventories and crafting grids.

openeye.Description: Automatically collects and submits crash reports. Enable if asked or wish to help sort issues with the pack.

sampler.Description: ***Admin/diagnostic tool. Leave off unless asked to help test performance issues.

slice.Description: Custom client font based off of Chicago. Made by Falkreon.
